high_descs: Turn around and go to the front of the wooden desk in the right corner.
Pick up the phone on the left near the front edge of the desk.
Turn left and go to the side of the bed between the desk and the bed.
Place the phone on the bed on the left of the blue notebook in the middle.
Go around the desk back to the front of it.
Pick up the remaining phone on the desk.
Go back to the side of the bed between the desk and the bed.
Place the phone on the right of the blue notebook.
anns.task_desc: Move the phones from the desk to the bed.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to the wall, turn left, and walk to the desk.
Pick up the smartphone on the left.
Turn around, turn right, and walk to the bed.
Put the smartphone on the bed.
Turn around and walk to the desk.
Pick up the smartphone.
Turn left and walk to the bed.
Put the smartphone on the bed.
anns.task_desc: Put two smartphones on the bed.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the wall, then hang a left and walk up to the wooden desk.
Pick up the leftmost phone off of the desk.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and walk over to the end of the bed.
Put the phone on the bed standing up to the left of the leftmost blue book.
Walk back over to the wooden desk.
Pick up the phone off of the wooden desk.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the end of the bed.
Put the phone on the bed to the right of the leftmost blue book.
anns.task_desc: Move two phones to a bed.
